        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Immunoelectron microscopy using DAB in rat brain slices show that IP3R3 is present within some neuronal terminals in the brain, some of which are characterized by the presence of large dense core vesicles.\n\n16/3/2017 Pim\n- I chose term ER over SER because \"smooth\" is not mentioned in the paper.. Experimental description: \"Rats were deeply anesthetizedand then perfused with freshly prepared 4% paraformaldehyde...\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0030176 replaced by GO:0005789" ;
